duties_responsibilities.duty: Develop and maintain data mapping specifications based on the results of data analysis and functional requirements.
Design and build automated Extract, Transform & Load (ETL) jobs based on data mapping specifications.
Analyze reference datasets and be familiar with Master Data Management (MDM) tools.
Adhere to DevOps processes and work with application developers on system development life system functions.

education_certification.credential: A baccalaureate degree (or equivalent) in computer science or a related field, and two (2) years of full-time software experience, including one year in a project leader capacity.
